metadata.name: Passing the 0xTorch
metadata.description: Realizing our imagination has always intrigued us as people. From legos in the physical world to the wild success of Minecraft in the digital. Roblox furthered our ability to share these creations. And Sandbox will show us the value of them. As computing power increases we reach ever closer to our artistic potential. In the background a synthetic approximation of a brain dreams about those worlds. We pass the torch along to those with new ideas so they can light the way towards a brighter future.
